 mass-spring mechanical systems, an electric circuit, and a\nnonholonomic mechanical system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 30 Apr 2011 18:03:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Oct 2013 05:55:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-04-29"}
